          <ul>
            <li><strong>Must be obtained locally</strong> - from Sault Ste. Marie Police Service</li>
            <li><strong>Verifies suitability</strong> - ensures no relevant criminal history</li>
            <li><strong>Required for all applicants</strong> - owner/operator must submit</li>
            <li><strong>Processing time varies</strong> - apply early</li>
          </ul>

