            <li><strong>$2,000,000 minimum</strong> liability coverage</li>
            <li><strong>City as additional insured</strong> - requires specific policy endorsement</li>
            <li><strong>Certificate required</strong> with application</li>
            <li><strong>Maintain continuously</strong> throughout license term</li>
          </ul>

