          <ul>
            <li><strong>Give neighbors your contact info</strong> before operating</li>
            <li><strong>Enables direct communication</strong> - issues resolved before escalation</li>
            <li><strong>Builds community relationships</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Reduces formal complaints</strong></li>
          </ul>

